thread.title: Speedos hosting meet this weekend

author: DALE STRODE
title: Speedos hosting meet this weekend
text: Smaller Larger Related Media Youth swimmers from across the Western Slope will flock to Aspen this weekend for the annual Aspen Speedos Invitational swim meet at the Aspen Recreation Center (ARC). The local Aspen Speedos junior swim club will host the competition, which will kick off at noon Saturday. The swimmers will compete through 6 p.m. Saturday at the ARC. On Sunday, the junior swimmers will compete from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m. at the ARC pool. Traditionally, visiting swim clubs travel to Aspen from Grand Junction, Montrose, Durango, Glenwood Springs, Steamboat Springs and beyond.
